yingyinNormal.en: It would be unusual. I get that. I get not everybody could do that, but everybody's not us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那，那会很不寻常的，我懂。我知道不是每个人都会那么做，但是那些人不是我们

yingyinNormal.en: I didn't, actually. Aconitine. Aconitine. Unusual choice for an assassination. Tends to stay in the bloodstream.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我还没说，乌头碱。乌头碱，很不寻常的暗杀手段，很容易残留在血液中。

yingyinNormal.en: Air travel is so common today that our airways are filled with all kinds of travelers , some of them more unusual than others.
yingyinNormal.zh: 空中旅行变得如此普通了，我们的航空路线到处都是旅行者，其中有那么一些不寻常的。

yingyinNormal.en: Really? Because every time we've talked about unusual animal genitals, you've always had some pretty strong and controversial opinions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是吗？每次我们谈到不寻常的动物生殖器，你总会有些有力且富争议性的观点。

yingyinNormal.en: And in chemistry, no less. And wouldn't that be unusual? Because you're a physicist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过是化学奖，这是不是很不寻常呢？因为你是个物理学家。

yingyinNormal.en: Was there anything unusual about how you found her? To warrant an official investigation?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们在她身上发现了什么特别之处么？以至于要让警方开始调查？

yingyinNormal.en: Remember, nobody is in a hurry here, so take your time and expect some unusual road closures!
yingyinNormal.zh: 请记住，保持悠闲的心情，所以你需要预留时间，并预期会出现意外的道路封闭。

yingyinNormal.en: And Rebecca? I mean, I only ask because it's a little unusual for the father to be here alone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 丽贝卡怎么样？我这幺问是因为父亲一般不会单独带孩子来医院。

yingyinNormal.en: In the far northwestern province of Xinjiang, they are employing a 2,000-year old invention to harness the unusual climactic conditions across these enormous plains: wind power.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在遥远西北地区的新疆省，他们采用了一种已有两千年历史的古老发明，以利用这非凡的横跨整个辽阔平原的气候条件。正是风力。

yingyinNormal.en: When my father started, they had a handful of chemicals, 1 or 2 or 3. Now it's not unusual for us to have 40 or 50 products available, because without that, the yields will suffer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我爸爸刚开始创业时他们使用数量很少的化学药品1或者2或者3种，现在我们以已经经常使用40或者50种药物了，因为要是不那样做会对土地造成损害。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, the update should prevent any further voices, but you will let me know if any of the hosts display or exhibit any unusual behavior, won't you, Bernard? Yes, of course. Good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总之，程序升级应该能阻止一切幻听了，但是如果有任何接待员有异常表现，都要告诉我，伯纳德。好的，当然了。好。

yingyinNormal.en: 400 miles away, deep in the heart to the Hunan Province is another epic holy site, but this time formed without human hands. A natural formation shaped by the area's unusual geology, Tian Men Shan, known as the heavens gate cave.
yingyinNormal.zh: 六百四十公里开外，在湖南省的腹地，坐落着另一个史诗级圣地，但是这回却并非出自人类手笔，而是大自然的鬼斧神工。天门山，也即通往天堂的大门。

yingyinNormal.en: In the situation with the obnoxious-football-fan-turned-good-samaritan, your brain says, "Well, in my experience, pretty much anyone would lend someone their umbrella, but the way this guy acted at the football game, that was unusual."
yingyinNormal.zh: 在那个情况讨厌的足球迷最后成了好心人，你的大脑说：「嗯，根据我的经验很多人都可以借别人雨伞，但是这个人在足球场的举止却只有他会这样。」
